OL,3,CHigher than expected jump in inflation
OL,4,Cto 3% may not be as bad as it looks
OL,6,FA major driver of inflation was the
OL,7,FVAT which the government slapped on
OL,8,Fprivate school fees from January, ITV
OL,9,FNews' Political Correspondent Carl
OL,10,FDinnen explains
OL,12,FThe jump in Consumer Prices Index
OL,13,F(CPI) inflation to 3% has taken
OL,14,Fanalysts a little by surprise (it was
OL,15,Fexpected to hit 2.8%). But it may not
OL,16,Fbe quite as bad as it looks.
OL,18,FThe rise in food and non-alcoholic
OL,19,Fdrink inflation to 3.3% is definitely
OL,20,Fconcerning because it hits the poorest
OL,21,Fhouseholds the hardest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
