OL,3,CHigher than expected jump in inflation
OL,4,Cto 3% may not be as bad as it looks
OL,6,FBut the other two big drivers of this
OL,7,Fjump are unlikely to have the same
OL,8,Feffect next month.
OL,10,FOne is airfares - usually those take-
OL,11,Foff dramatically in December and then
OL,12,Fplunge back down again in January.
OL,14,FBut for technical reasons the price
OL,15,Fincrease in December 2024 was nowhere
OL,16,Fnear as pronounced as usual and so the
OL,17,Fsubsequent drop in January 2025 was
OL,18,Falso smaller.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
