OL,3,CHigher than expected jump in inflation
OL,4,Cto 3% may not be as bad as it looks
OL,6,FAnother major driver was the VAT which
OL,7,Fthe government slapped on private
OL,8,Fschool fees from January. That pushed
OL,9,Fthose up by a hefty 13%.
OL,11,FAlthough some of that effect might
OL,12,Fstill be felt next month (depending on
OL,13,Fwhen the bills go through), it is
OL,14,Fgenerally considered a one-off effect
OL,15,Fas a result of a policy decision and
OL,16,Ftherefore not integral to the overall
OL,17,Finflationary picture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
